                <li><strong>Domain Name System (DNS) Checks:</strong> Verify that the domain part of the email address has valid DNS records (A, AAAA, MX records). This doesn't guarantee the email exists but rules out completely bogus domains.</li>
                <li><strong>Blacklists/Whitelists:</strong> Maintain lists of known disposable email providers, spam domains, or legitimate domains to enhance validation.</li>
