                </p>
                <p>
                    Each click handler:
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Reads</strong> the current value (e.g., <code>0</code>).</li>
                        <li>Starts an <strong>asynchronous delay</strong> (simulated by <code>setTimeout</code>).</li>
                        <li><strong>After the delay</strong>, increments its *own* read value (e.g., <code>0 + 1 = 1</code>).</li>
                        <li><strong>Writes</strong> this new value back to the display.</li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
                <p>
