        <h3>The Consequences:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Inaccurate Totals:</strong> When you add or subtract these inexact representations, the tiny errors accumulate. This leads to sums that are slightly off, sometimes by a tiny fraction (e.g., <code>14.999999999999998</code> or <code>15.000000000000001</code> instead of <code>15.00</code>).</li>
